OL,3,CMan who died at Cardiff recycling site
OL,4,Cnamed
OL,6,FColleagues of a man who died at a
OL,7,Frecycling site in Cardiff have
OL,8,Fdescribed him as a "totally
OL,9,Firreplaceable" friend who was "always
OL,10,Fwilling to help".
OL,12,FEmergency services were called to
OL,13,Freports of an injured man at the
OL,14,FAtlantic Recycling site on Newton Road
OL,15,Fin the city on Monday afternoon, July
OL,16,F8.
