OL,6,FPolice later confirmed the man - who
OL,7,Fwas a contractor carrying out
OL,8,Fmaintenance at the site - had died of
OL,9,Fhis injuries and his family had been
OL,10,Finformed.
OL,12,FSouth Wales Police confirmed that a
OL,13,Fjoint investigation is now underway
OL,14,Fbetween them and the Health and Safety
OL,15,FExecutive to establish the
OL,16,Fcircumstances surrounding the incident.
OL,18,FThe man has now been named locally as
OL,19,FKyle Colcomb.
