OL,6,FIn a statement posted online, M&B
OL,7,FHydraulics said: "We are sad to say
OL,8,FKyle was tragically taken in an on
OL,9,Fsite incident at a site in Cardiff.
OL,11,F"We are all absolutely devastated at
OL,12,Fthe loss of Kyle, who was an
OL,13,Foutstanding fitter an absolute
OL,14,Fgentleman and an all around nice guy.
OL,15,FTotally irreplaceable. Absolute
OL,16,Fpleasure to have worked with you and
OL,17,Fhave know you RIP OUR FRIEND. Our
OL,18,Fthoughts go out to all his family at
OL,19,Fthis terrible time."
