OL,7,Ftribute to share their memories of Mr
OL,8,FColcomb.
OL,10,FOne Facebook user said: "Can't believe
OL,11,Fthis has happened... Kyle was a lovely
OL,12,Flad, being new to the job when he came
OL,13,Fto site we would aways give him a
OL,14,Fhand. Thinking of you all guys at this
OL,15,Fsad time condolences go out to Kyle's
OL,16,Ffamily."
